          "expr": "sum by (service) (rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{service=~\"admin-api|student-api|actor-host\",status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / sum by (service) (rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{service=~\"admin-api|student-api|actor-host\"}[5m]))",
